Phase-4a prescribed-test relativistic pusher evidence replay commands
===================================================================

Kernel helper release:
  /tmp/athenak-cr-phase4a-pusher-kernel/src/athena \
    -i inputs/unit_tests/cr_relativistic_pusher_kernel.athinput

Kernel helper debug:
  /tmp/athenak-cr-phase4a-pusher-kernel-debug/src/athena \
    -i inputs/unit_tests/cr_relativistic_pusher_kernel.athinput

Production-path analytical and convergence suite:
  python3 scripts/particles/cr_relativistic_pusher_runtime_inspect.py \
    --binary /tmp/athenak-cr-phase4a-pusher-runtime/src/athena \
    --input inputs/unit_tests/cr_relativistic_pusher_runtime.athinput \
    --criteria docs/source/modules/figures/cr_tracer_relativistic_acceleration/cr_relativistic_phase4a_preregistered_criteria.json \
    --work-dir /tmp/athenak-cr-phase4a-runtime-suite-final \
    --metrics /tmp/phase4a_pusher_runtime_metrics.json

Parser contract:
  cd /tmp/athenak-cr-phase4a-cpu/src
  python3 -m pytest -q \
    /Users/dbf75/.codex/worktrees/e354/athenak-DF/tst/test_suite/particles/test_particles_cr_relativistic_contract_cpu.py

Retained legacy regressions:
  cd tst
  python3 run_test_suite.py --test test_suite/particles/test_particles_cr_cpu.py --cpu
  python3 run_test_suite.py --test test_suite/particles/test_particles_cr_accuracy_cpu.py --cpu
  python3 run_test_suite.py --test test_suite/particles/test_particles_cr_mpicpu.py --mpicpu
  python3 run_test_suite.py --test test_suite/particles/test_particles_cr_accuracy_mpicpu.py --mpicpu
  python3 run_test_suite.py --style

Explicit MPI rejection probe:
  cmake -S . -B /tmp/athenak-cr-phase4a-pusher-runtime-mpi \
    -D PROBLEM=unit_tests/cr_relativistic_pusher_runtime_test \
    -D Athena_ENABLE_MPI=ON \
    -D Kokkos_ENABLE_SERIAL=ON
  cmake --build /tmp/athenak-cr-phase4a-pusher-runtime-mpi -j 4
  mpirun -n 2 /tmp/athenak-cr-phase4a-pusher-runtime-mpi/src/athena \
    -i inputs/unit_tests/cr_relativistic_pusher_runtime.athinput \
    mesh/nx1=16 \
    meshblock/nx1=8

